rsAtmMib.name: rsAtmMib

revisions.description: Initial version of of Riverstone extensions to ATM Management.

rsAtmMib.contactinfo: Riverstone Networks, Inc 5200 Great America Parkway Santa Clara CA USA 95054 PHONE:+1 408.878.6500 EMAIL: nms-eng@riverstonenet.com WEB: http://www.riverstonenet.com
rsAtmMib.description: This MIB module defines enterprise extensions to IETF Standard MIB modules. rsAtmFdbObjects group defines a mapping from a MAC address to the ATM PVC on which it was learned. Copyright (C) Riverstone Networks, Inc 2001

rsAtmFdbMacsLearned.name: rsAtmFdbMacsLearned
rsAtmFdbMacsLearned.description: Number of MAC addresses learned on ATM line cards system.

rsAtmFdbTable.name: rsAtmFdbTable
rsAtmFdbTable.description: This table provides a mapping of a MAC address to the bridge port, plus Virtual Path Identifier/Virtual Channel Identifier (VPI/VCI) on which it was learned. A row will appear in this table for each row in dot1dTpFdbTable that maps to a bridge port (dot1dBasePortNum) which is of type ATM ifType(37). Rows in this table share the same fate as rows in dot1dTpFdbTable.

rsAtmFdbEntry.name: rsAtmFdbEntry
rsAtmFdbEntry.description: An entry in the table shares the same fate as an entry in dot1dTpFdbTable and uses the same indexing.

rsAtmFdbVpi.name: rsAtmFdbVpi
rsAtmFdbVpi.description: The Virtual Path Identifier on which this MAC address was learned.

rsAtmFdbVci.name: rsAtmFdbVci
rsAtmFdbVci.description: The Virtual Channel Identifier on which this MAC address was learned.

rsAtmFdbBaseGroup.name: rsAtmFdbBaseGroup
rsAtmFdbBaseGroup.description: A collection of objects providing a mapping between a MAC address and the ATM vpi/vci it was learned on.

rsAtmFdbMibCompliance.name: rsAtmFdbMibCompliance
rsAtmFdbMibCompliance.description: The compliance statement for device support of extension to dot1dTpFdbTable for ATM interfaces.
